issue.title: Thank you!
issue.body:
I found this library while implementing ADR in a new project. I do love your idea so much that I'm going to implement this in phpDocumentor and make it a feature of the tool. 

Allowing people to check their ADR directly from the documentation in their project. Thank you very much for this wonderfull project!

comment.body: Thank you for your kind words! I'm glad that you found the idea useful. :)
